jawai maaza bhala ( marathi : जावई माझा भला ; translation : my good son-in-law ) is a marathi film that was released on 16 march 2008 . the film was written by ratnakar matkari , directed by adwait dadarkar and presented by kalashri boston . the film stars vikram gokhale , amita khopkar , jayant savarkar , sujata joshi and rajashri tope . the film is based on a what a father goes through just before his daughter is about to get married .